      "page_number": 0,
      "content": "Welcome to WHAT DO THEY SAY? This book will help you learn about all sorts of animal sounds. We are going to meet many friends who have something wonderful to say!",
      "source_page_number": 0,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_000.jpg",
