        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "content": "Woof! Woof! The puppy is jumping high with great energy. He happily leaps, barking loudly and declaring, \"Let's play!\" We know that playtime must end, so we search for the next friend.",
      "source_page_number": 1,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_001.jpg",
        "filename": "page_001.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_4/page_001.mp3",
        "filename": "page_001.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "content": "Next up is a hungry cat near a milk bowl. The cat meows softly and tells everyone, \"Meow... Meow... The cat says: \\\"I am hungry!\\\"\" We wait patiently to see which creature greets us next.",
      "source_page_number": 2,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_002.jpg",
        "filename": "page_002.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_4/page_002.mp3",
        "filename": "page_002.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "content": "Look at the yellow bird perched happily on a branch. He chirps out clearly and sings, \"Tweet! Tweet! The cheerful bird says, \\\"Good morning!\\\"\" Following his lovely greeting, we see another animal in the field.",
      "source_page_number": 3,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_003.jpg",
        "filename": "page_003.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_4/page_003.mp3",
        "filename": "page_003.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "content": "The story continues with a big brown cow standing gently. She makes her sound and speaks kindly: \"Mooo! The cow says, \\\"Hello, friend.\\\"\" This friendly greeting guides us toward a playful puddle.",
      "source_page_number": 4,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_004.jpg",
        "filename": "page_004.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_4/page_004.mp3",
        "filename": "page_004.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "A little yellow duckling waddles to the water puddle. It makes splashing sounds as it calls out, \"Quack! Quack! The duck says: \\\"Follow me!\\\"\" After playing in the stream, we spot a truly mighty and strong creature.",
      "source_page_number": 5,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_005.jpg",
        "filename": "page_005.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_4/page_005.mp3",
        "filename": "page_005.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 6,
      "content": "See this powerful lion sitting up tall with his big mane? He roars loudly and proclaims with strength: \"ROAR! The lion says: \\\"I am strong!\\\"\" We have seen so many impressive animals today. Let us listen to all the wonderful sounds now.",
      "source_page_number": 6,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_006.jpg",
        "filename": "page_006.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_4/page_006.mp3",
        "filename": "page_006.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 7,
      "content": "Woof! Meow! Tweet! Roar! All these amazing animals shared their unique voices with us. What do you think of them? Now it is your turn; what do YOU say?",
      "source_page_number": 7,
